com.serena.dmclient.api
Class BaselineDetails

java.lang.Object
  com.serena.dmclient.api.BaselineDetails
All Implemented Interfaces:
DimensionsLcObjectDetails, DimensionsObjectDetails
public class BaselineDetails
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains details of a new baseline that is to be created. It does not perform any validation, but is merely a data object to pass to the create baseline operation, which will validate it and then act on it.
